title: GameMaker-Studio Auto-Updater BETA 1
description:
Here's the first beta of my auto-updater, finally out of experimental builds.

Please know that this is a beta and may have bugs. I have found the releases to be stable enough for a beta, so here it is.

I have changed update servers, this should hopefully resolve issues with people not being able to connect to the update server.

Note: You must do a clean install, pleases uninstall any previous versions you may have through the CP and use the cleanup tool provided before installing.

Changelog:

Logging improvements 
Added maintenance mode 
Added blacklist mode 
Changed update server to new location 
Updated icons 
various performance improvements

Enjoy
